      • dAxes

        public dAxes(DVector origin,
             DVector inX,
             DVector inY,
             DVector inZ,
             boolean forceOrthoNormality,
             AbstractAxes parent)
        Parameters:
        origin - the center of this axes basis. The basis vector parameters will be automatically ADDED to the origin in order to create this basis vector.
        inX - the direction of the X basis vector in global coordinates, given as an offset from this base's origin in global coordinates.
        inY - the direction of the Y basis vector in global coordinates, given as an offset from this base's origin in global coordinates.
        inZ - the direction of the Z basis vector in global coordinates, given as an offset from this base's origin in global coordinates.
        forceOrthoNormality -
